QuestData.Title: Wet Work
QuestData.Description: Listen carefully, $c.$b$bThere are three leaders in this region who are commanding the elves, keeping their focus directed on the lumber camp. Slaying them will certainly cause panic and disarray, hopefully enough for us to successfully complete our mission.$b$bWhile you're at it, bringing down their scouts can only aid our cause.
QuestData.LogDescription: Krokk wants you to kill Dorinar, Arminon, Endolar, and 12 Ashenvale Scouts.
QuestData.RewardText: Well done, $c.$b$bThey're in complete disarray. Just look at them!
